{
  "title": "ISic003719. A stone bread-stamp(?)",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span class=\"textpartnumber\">face a</span>  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μ ((plough))\n                    \n                    η\n                    ((jug))\n                    νία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μ ((plough))\n                    \n                    η\n                    ((jug))\n                    νία\">Μ ((plough)) <span class=\"textpartnumber\">face b</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>η <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>((jug)) <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>νία</span></span>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\">face d</span>  <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span> εὖ <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>((amphora)) <span class=\"textpartnumber\">face d</span>  <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>((dolphin)) <span class=\"textpartnumber\">face e</span>  <br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>((swastika)) <span class=\"textpartnumber\">face f</span>  <br id=\"al9-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span><span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ἡ͡ρ͡έ͡α</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span class=\"textpartnumber\">face a</span><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μ ((plough))\n                    \n                    η\n                    ((jug))\n                    νία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μ ((plough))\n                    \n                    η\n                    ((jug))\n                    νία\">Μ()<span class=\"textpartnumber\">face b</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>Η<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>()<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΝΙΑ</span></span><span class=\"textpartnumber\">face d</span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΕΥ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>()<span class=\"textpartnumber\">face d</span><br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>()<span class=\"textpartnumber\">face e</span><br id=\"al8-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>()<span class=\"textpartnumber\">face f</span><br id=\"al9-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span><span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Η͡Ρ͡Ε͡Α</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Manganaro</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Manganaro argues that this is a bread stamp, and connects the letters of the first two sides to form the name of one of the two bakers, along with that on side f.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 51.1395 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Manganaro 2001 192 figs.23-27 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001805\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001805</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
